{"title":"The Sour Bicycles Bad Granny Pre-Order","link":"https://theradavist.com/the-sour-bicycles-bad-granny-pre-order/","date":1732722001000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Sour-Bikes-Bad-Granny-Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Sour-Bikes-Bad-Granny-Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Sour-Bikes-Bad-Granny-Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Sour-Bikes-Bad-Granny-Singlespeed-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>As covered in our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2023-made-bike-show-coverage-part-02/\" target=\"_blank\">2023 MADE Reportage</a>, the <a href=\"https://sour.bike/bikes/mtb/bad-granny/\" target=\"_blank\">Sour Bicycles Bad Granny</a> rigid MTB frameset (1,099 € ) is up for grabs in a pre-order. Read on for all the details as the order window closure is approaching…</em><span></span></p>\n<h3><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?fit=1200,1600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?resize=1200,750&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?resize=2000,1250&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?resize=768,480&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?resize=1536,960&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-07.jpg?resize=2048,1280&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></h3>\n<h3>Bad Granny Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>1,099 € frame and fork</li>\n<li>S-L sizing (geo below)</li>\n<li>Headtube: 44mm, ZS44/EC44</li>\n<li>Bottom bracket: 73mm BSA with eccentric shell for singlespeed</li>\n<li>Rear spacing: 12mm x 148mm Boost, thru axle</li>\n<li>Seatpost: 31.6mm</li>\n<li>Rear brake: PM7″ disc</li>\n<li>Fork travel: Rigid, but will accept 100mm – 120mm</li>\n<li>Wheel sizes: 27.5″ or 29″</li>\n<li>Tire clearance: 27.5 x 2.4″, 29 x 2.4″</li>\n<li>Stealth dropper post cable routing</li>\n<li>Second top tube for better power transfer (go fast)</li>\n<li>Rigid fork with SAG-o-meter for comfort and precise steering (don’t crash)</li>\n<li>Sram Transmission ready Dropouts (“UDH”)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-06.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-06.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-05.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-05.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>A Proper Modern Do-It-All Klunker</h3>\n<p>Klunkers were the first mountain bikes, developed after the onset of Mountain Cruisers in Marin County. The Bad Granny was inspired by the ingenuity of these early tinkerers and mountain bike framebuilders. As such, it’s got all the bases covered. Belt drive? Cool. There is a split seat stay. Singlespeed? No worries. There’s an eccentric bottom bracket. SRAM Transmission? Got you. There’s a UDH-ready dropout design.</p>\n<p>The Bad Granny can be whatever you want it to be.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-03.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-03.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>Sizes S/M through L/XL allow for the rider to achieve proper fit by adjusting stem length and bar rise. A 74º seat tube angle and 68º heat tube angle put the Bad Granny into a perfect “all-rounder/XC” geometrical sweet spot, making it at home on gravel roads and swoopy singletrack. Add a dropper to engage the fun.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-04.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-04.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-04.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-04.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-09.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-09.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-09.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-09.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-010.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-010.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-010.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-010.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-08.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-08.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-08.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/11/Sour_Bad_Granny-08.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Bad Granny is <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/sour-bicycles-dresden-germany/\" target=\"_blank\">made in Germany</a> at Sour’s Factory and is available to <a href=\"https://sour.bike/shop/bikes/mtb/bad-granny-frame-set-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\">pre-order now</a>. See more info on the Bad Granny at <a href=\"https://sour.bike/bikes/mtb/bad-granny/\" target=\"_blank\">Sour Bicycles.</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-sour-bicycles-bad-granny-pre-order/\">The Sour Bicycles Bad Granny Pre-Order</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"939088c0994e6fbbc84da2b28f3e393a49653877f39c499910c5f73d65298392","category":"Cycling"}